definitions.definition: A rabbit , especially the European rabbit, Oryctolagus cuniculus (formerly known as Lepus cuniculus ).
Locally for other rabbit-like or hyrax-like animals, such as the Cape hyrax ( das , dassie ) or the pika ( Ochotona princeps , formerly Lagomys princeps ).

subdefinitions.definition: Used in the Old Testament as a translation of Hebrew שָׁפָן ( shafán ) , thought to be the rock hyrax ( Procavia capensis , syn. Hyrax syriacus ).

definitions.definition: A simpleton ; one who may be taken in by a cony-catcher .
An edible West Indian fish, a grouper given in different sources as: Epinephelus apua , the hind of Bermuda; nigger-fish , Epinephelus punctatus ; Cephalopholis fulva .
Any if certain members of family Epinephelidae of Atlantic groupers , such as mutton hamlets , graysby , Cuban coneys , and rooster hinds .
